---
title: "Buyer & Seller Guides"
description: "Plain-language guides to buying and selling in St. Petersburg — flood zones and insurance, neighborhoods, the real process and costs — written by a local broker."
permalink: /guides/
crumbs: []
---
{#- /guides/ — plan §2 #6 + §3b. Wave 2: this index renders FROM the KB
    (kb/guides/*.md via src/_data/kb.js) — live entries get cards + links,
    outline entries are listed as in-the-works WITHOUT links (an outline is a
    sourcing plan, not a page). Adding a guide = adding a kb entry; this page
    never edits by hand. -#}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">First-hand, not syndicated</p>
    <h1>Buyer &amp; seller guides</h1>
    <p class="lede lede--wide">The questions people actually ask about St. Pete real estate, answered with
    primary sources and broker experience &mdash; each guide carries a named author, its sources,
    and a visible last-verified date.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:10px"><a class="quiet" href="/ask/">Have a quick question instead? Ask Lane &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:10px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="grid grid--2">
      {%- for g in kb.guidesLive %}
      <div class="card">
        <p class="g-eyebrow" style="margin:0 0 6px">{{ g.eyebrow | replace("The knowledge base · ", "") }}</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem"><a href="/guides/{{ g.slug }}/">{{ g.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ g.description }}</p>
        <p class="fine" style="margin:8px 0 0">By {{ g.author }} &middot; last verified {{ g.last_verified | longDate }}</p>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>

    {%- if kb.guidesPlanned.length %}
    <div class="stub-block" style="margin-top:22px">
      <p style="margin-bottom:6px"><strong>In the works</strong> &mdash; researched, sourced, and
      broker-reviewed before each one publishes (nothing here auto-publishes):</p>
      <p style="margin:0">
      {%- for g in kb.guidesPlanned %}
      {{ loop.index + kb.guidesLive.length }}&middot; {{ g.title }}{% if not loop.last %} &nbsp;&nbsp; {% endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
      </p>
    </div>
    {%- endif %}
  </div>
</section>

{% set askLead = "Have a quick question instead of reading? Ask Lane &mdash; grounded answers from Everlane&rsquo;s knowledge base, with a real broker behind them." %}
{% include "components/ask-lane-module.njk" %}
